The sensitivity, response and recovery characteristics of the sensor device have been studied by measuring the change in resistance, in the ambient and reducing gas atmosphere. The gas detection sensitivity (S) of the sensor device has been evaluated using the relation:7S=(Ra−Rg)/Rg\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
